hopobject.body: I work for a publishers vlamorous RexMax46: Good post. Thanks for sharing. I would also add that without the public outrage this trial would never have taken place. But now that it has, what we know to be true makes it clear that a trial was necessary. This is true whether you believe Zimmerman is guilty or innocent. The point is, there are enough questionable circumstances surrounding this occurrence that a trial is warranted to bring out the truth as best we can.
